  "description": "Small things that complement Minecraft like Foods and Drinks, Blocks and Items, Texture and Tweaks",
  "body": "## This mod adds little things to complement the vanilla features and gameplay.\n\n***\n\n# 📖Features/Planned:\n\n✔ Foods and Drinks.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_198b291e-cf67-43fb-ab43-5748030a7588.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"488\" height=\"164\"></p></div>\n\n✔ Equipment.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p>- Void Totem:</p><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_788656be-74d3-48ba-987a-b0e9f72e04c5.gif\"></p><hr><p>- Copper Equipments (Backport 1.21.1):</p><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_e8fa032d-ac97-4f4a-b9cb-e94cf39a74bd.png\"></p></div>\n\n✔ Blocks.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p>- Building blocks:<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_6ac545bd-d7ae-494e-b390-b5dcb829b077.png\"></p></div>\n\n✔ Utilities.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p>- Reroll enchantments (v0.3.3 only):<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_ec2af750-5647-4f06-a83e-cbc9e5b3def2.gif\"><br>- Reroll trades (v0.3.3 only):<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_e14e4da4-a161-4e88-bd71-0715e788088f.gif\"></p></div>\n\n✔ Teaks / Misc.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p>- Thorns in Shield:<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_22e2eab3-b01f-44fa-a6d6-7dae58eff1d7.png\"></p><p>- Bread 2x2 crafting:</p><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_0ad2c3de-6ef6-4107-898f-436d9c9a6019.png\" alt=\"Bread 2x2 crafting\" width=\"237\" height=\"159\"></p><p>-Paper 2x2 crafting:</p><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_6500692a-645b-4fe5-af35-4d4df8b9a0b4.png\"></p><p>- Double doors:</p><p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_e1d649cc-bcb4-457b-bfb6-e7737281e192.gif\"></p><p>- Fireball:<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_3b569bde-f692-42d4-a96a-952279e6f3d1.gif\"></p></div>\n\n✔ Texture.\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><hr><p>- grass block of biomes is slightly saturated.</p><hr><p>- Low fire on the screen:<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1351479/description_3d0eb796-04ab-49cf-a18e-aef87a09bfae.gif\"></p><hr><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\n✖ Furniture.\n\n✖ Animations.\n\n✖ Automation.\n\n###### (✔ = added / ✖ = comming)\n\n***\n\nFeel free to add this mod to your modpack.\n\nPlease do not report issues in the comments.",
